data.description: 3 Bedroom 2 Bath home on several wooded lots with community boat ramp and fishing dock on Lake Cypress. Newer Roof, Plumbing, and Driveway all in 2021. New appliances in 2021.  Wireless ceiling fans, hard wired camera system, and Peoples Fiber Optic wired Internet. Hardwood floors with crown molding. Covered porch for outdoor entertaining or relaxing. Multiple buildings. Workshop and home office buildings have electricity and air conditioning. One lot has covered RV parking for 2 RVs. Outbuildings could be used for guest quarters, storage, or additional workspace.
